| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2451 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 491d07c6-0dab-5cb8-80a9-40f32b602a9c"
